14. An aqueous corrosion inhibited acid cleaning composition for inhibiting corrosion, the composition comprising:
(a) about 1 to about 30 wt. % aqueous sulfuric acid cleaning solution;
(b) about 5 to about 50 wt. % nitric acid;
(c) about 1 wt. % to about 80 wt. % water; and,
(d) up to about 5 weight % urea;
